uction telesat also manages the operations of additional satellites for third parties loral also owns  of xtar a joint venture between loral and hisdesat a consortium comprised of leading spanish telecommunications companies including hispasat sa and agencies of the spanish government through its xtareur satellite xtar provides xband services to government users in the united states spain and other allied countries including the us department of state the spanish ministry of defence and danish armed forces xtars headquarters are in ashburn va note information on this site contains forwardlooking statements within the meaning of section a of the securities act of  as amended and section e of the securities exchange act of  as amended in addition from time to time loral space  communications inc or its representatives have made or may make forwardlooking statements orally or in writing such forwardlooking statements may be included in but are not limited to various filings made by the company with the securities and exchange commission press releases or oral statements made with the approval of an authorized executive officer of the company actual results could differ materially from those projected or suggested in any forwardlooking statements as a result of a wide variety of factors and conditions these factors and conditions have been described in various filings made by the company with the securities and exchange commission investor alerts contact ir request information faqs telesat xtar company board of directors executive officers telesat executive team investors stock information shareholder services corporate governance financials  filings events investor resources news loral news telesat news careers faqs contact us site map loral space  communications all rights reserved powered by q inc  opens in new window loral space  communications inc  careers skip to main content homecareers print page email page careers at loral consider a career with loral space  co